data.title: 准备以至少20秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: Well, due to a random combination of genes, I ended up looking like a cross between my mom and dad. I am softer looking than my mother and harder-edged in personality. I am less stubborn than my father, but I have cheekbones and a prominent chin. I have my mother’s hair color, my father’s skin color. I have a nose that looks somewhere between the two. I am of average height. I am not tiny and skinny like my mom. I am not tall like my dad. I am not overweight like my aunts on my father’s side. I escaped the worst of the mental illness on my mother’s side. I inherited my father’s chronic kidney stones. I do not know how it works. I think genetics are weird. (130 words)
data.referenceText: Whom do you most resemble in your family? In what ways do you resemble this person?
data.referenceTranslate: 你在家里最像谁? 你在哪些方面像这个人?
